    <content lang="en">
      <city>Bern</city>
      <title>Surplus of 1.7 billion in federal consolidated financial statements for 2015</title>
      <lead>During its meeting today, the Federal Council approved the consolidated financial statements for 2015. The financial situation of the central and decentralized units of the Confederation remains good, with a surplus of CHF 1.7 billion generated for the year.</lead>
